    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>New BFF endpoint adding ~150 LOC of streaming/zip code. ADR-007 (SpeFileStore facade), ADR-008 (endpoint filter), ADR-010 (DI minimalism), ADR-019 (ProblemDetails), ADR-029 (publish hygiene + NFR-06) all binding. BFF additions governance (Placement Justification) required.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>E</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
